    `notidata.rbis_noti_time_fail_wk_&ymd.` is a PERMANENT dated SAS dataset
    (the `notidata` libname points at a real on-disk path, not WORK) -- it
    is not just exported to Excel, it is also persisted in its own right.
    An earlier draft of this conversion only wrote the Excel rendition and
    silently dropped the persistent dated dataset; fixed here by also
